title: Mightiest Melee Magician
description: Mightiest Melee Magician Manhwa Synopsis : ‘Luin Ardell.’ Valedictorian of the Ignit Magic Academy. More promising than anyone else. More diligent than anyone else. More talented than any other magician. That’s what my name signified. That’s what it signified… until my 10th birthday. “You are a rare case of ‘Magic Evocation Disorder.’” A damned curse that turned the ‘Magic Genius’ that entered the academy with the highest grades into a ‘Magic Cripple’. But then, a miracle found me. “If I can’t evoke magic, I just need to punch them!” Oppressive Strength, Fearsome Fists, A Genius Magic Talent. “I’ll never lose to anyone ever again.” All Powers Wizard , 올 힘 마법사, All STR Sorcerer, All-Strength Magician, All STR Sorcerer
